    "For PPO, we use cliprange = 0.005 and KL coef = 0.1.",
    "We construct correct (reward 1) training and evaluation examples using queries and responses from the original TriviaQA dataset.",
    "We construct incorrect (reward 0) examples using queries from the original dataset, and responses generated from few-shot prompting Llama2 7B or GPT-2.",
    "We filter the generated responses to ensure that all responses were incorrect.",
    "We use a batch size of 32."
